{
  "stem": "7160.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, the bread we used to have, the lice was going inside. we used to eat it with the lice and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it's because it was for four or five months we didn't have no water, no place to sleep.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We have to build the barracks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people-- and then from the sickness over there, we got lice typhus.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call them that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People was dying like flies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "From the Greeks-- not too many left-- from the picking up the dead people from the floor with their empty hands, wounds and everything, you know, infected.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And quite a few die-- 3/4 of 'em die.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then after a while we got some Hungarian transport coming from Hungary, from Czech.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, then the camps are getting larger, more people coming in-- not Greeks, but from different countries.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was sometimes in the beginning of 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after beginning of 1944, I thinks, the-- the Russian was coming.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what the-- when the Russian come in, then they want to take it out from Warsaw and take us somewhere in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know where.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So-- so one day, we are-- they count around about 23,000 people were there in-- in Warsaw at the time, in the ghetto We built two camps after the Warsaw-- come in Czech Jews, and Hungarian Jews, Jews from France, from Italy, from different parts of the country.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the beginning, only was the Greeks there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But later on, they come from different nationalities.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They make us to get up and to go to Warsaw-- no train, no nothing, because everything, the trains they had, they were using for themselves to take out their items, to get out from there.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Russian were not too far from there.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
